#

Crispy Potato Skins

40 min
$8
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairySoy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

SnackAppetizerComfort Food

Description

Deliciously crispy potato skins topped with cheese and bacon, perfect for snacking or as a side dish.

Ingredients

  • russet potatoes: 4 large
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • cheddar cheese: 1 cup, shredded
  • bacon bits: 1/2 cup
  • sour cream: 1/2 cup
  • green onions: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • paprika: 1 teaspoon
  • garlic powder: 1/2 teaspoon
